dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents roads for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2019.[This data set consists of digital map files containing road centerline information obtained predominantly by conducting field work using GPS technology and Orthophotography. Features contained in the data set include all road centerlines countywide and associated attributes.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This data is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data set was created as a foundational element for the Lincoln County Land Information System. The road centerline feature class provides a digital representation of all named private drives, streets, county roads, state highways, and federal highways within Lincoln County.]
